MediaDevilry is a working name for a new service for image
manipulation written in node.js.

== Planned features ==

* Rotation to arbitrary orientations
* Cropping

== Possible features ==

* Filters
** Sharpening
** Blurring
** Hue changes

== Support targets ==

* Use in MediaWiki as source for new images
* Use in MediaWiki as source for image edits
* Use in MediaWiki in inline file transclusions
